SC-5
Minimum Experience:
3 Years(Overall, at least three years of progressively responsible experience in the field of geographic information system, emergency mapping, spatial data analysis in particular context of education, food security, vulnerability analysis, emergency response mapping, humanitarian operations, or a closely related area. At least one year at G4 level or equivalent)
